Fix -d/-es CLI flags not applied during search (2026-06-26)

Root cause: g_mid_depth_override and g_end_depth_override were set by
option.hpp but never read by get_level() in level.hpp. The function
get_level_depth() that reads them existed but was never called anywhere.

Also fixes timing: tim() returns milliseconds, but the GTP stats divided
by 1000 (converting ms to seconds). Removed the /1000 division.

Changes:
1. level.hpp: Move globals before get_level(), use them to override depth/ES
2. option.hpp: Add #include "../engine/level.hpp" (was missing, globals undeclared)
3. gtp_command.hpp: Fix time_ms (was result.time/1000, should be result.time)

